snippet: The father of a woman who once dated NFL receiver Brandon Marshall called for the league's commissioner to resign Wednesday because he's disappointed in the way his daughter's abuse allegations were handled....

headline.print_headline: Father: NFL Mishandled My Daughter's Abuse Case
headline.main: Father: NFL Mishandled My Daughter's Abuse Case

lead_paragraph: The father of a woman who once dated NFL receiver Brandon Marshall called for the league's commissioner to resign Wednesday because he's disappointed in the way his daughter's abuse allegations were handled.
